    public class CsvSchema
extends com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.messaging.repeaters.BaseRepeater
    An ordered collection of CsvColumn objects, specifying the structure of a line in a CSV (Comma Separated Data) file. CsvColumn objects are passed to the constructor, CsvSchema(com.telenav.kivakit.data.formats.csv.CsvColumn<?>...) or added with add(CsvColumn). Columns are assigned indexes in the order that they are added. The columns can then be retrieved by name with columnForName(String).
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
